<!DOCTYPE html>
<html >
     <head >
          <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
     </head >
     <body >
          <p>
              Hi <%= @seeker.name %>,<br/><br/>
              <%= @finder.name %> may have found your lost item: <%= @item["title"] %>...<br/><br/>
              &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Found item details:
              &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<ul>
                <li>Date lost: <%= @item["date"] %></li>
                <li>Time lost: <%= @item["time"] %></li>
                <li>Place lost: <%= @item["place"] %></li>
                <li>Extra info: <%= @item["extra_info"] %></li>
              </ul>
              Please email <%= @finder.email %> to confirm it's yours, and arrange for its return.<br/><br/><br/>
              We hope your item is returned soon,<br/><br/>
              Team Oomerang<br/><br/>
              <hr>
              Item returned? Please delete it from your Oomerang dashboard.<br/><br/>

              Lost it? Found it? <a href="http://www.oomerang.it">Oomerang.it</a>!<br/>
          </p>
     </body >
</html>
